translation.Name: Banjo Memorial #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Banjo you were the greatest friend, family member, and pet I could ever ask for.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: You were always there for me, and I wish I could've be there for you when you passed away.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: I would give anything to be with you and to feel you purr one more time.
